race.comment: PLATINUM GIFT (2) has gotten better with each run this time in work and looks to be building up to another victory. Ready for the step-up in trip now and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. BEST COFFEE (1) is one from one over this course and distance and has been just behind the placegetters of late. No reason why he cannot find winning ways. BEAT HOLLOW (4) gets a stack of weight relief with the 4kg claim and maps ideally from gate two. Top-three candidate. WANT TO BE PROUD (3) doesn't win out of turn but is usually thereabouts and is a must for the multiples. GERRY'S PICK (7) broke the maiden status at the latest effort and will have taken some confidence from that victory. Can go right on with the job now.
